-06-21T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"知唔知邊方面壓力好大？有無方法避得開？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"錢 愛情 事業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點避"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"愛情應該係互相支撐，或者你講下係咪有咩事？<br />\n<br />\n事業係而家呢份工唔滿意？定未搵到工？<br />\n<br />\n錢就無得避㗎啦，唯一可以做嘅就係唔好睇到錢咁重。知易行難，加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323776a8535aab7fde6d2fec1b677b67ad24b4d6","tid":710774,"uid":138187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ab98f188c56cefbf70168bbaa54636b08ff61b","tid":710774,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"有冇咩減壓方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再咁落去跳樓仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"做meditation 一路聽啲慢歌<br />\n真係有用架"}]}